descriptionHTML:
--- Available also as a Phone Widget and Live Wallpaper! ---

Many Icons. So great watch face.
So stuffed with lots of icons that randomly change to keep your watch face busy each minute.
Choose the background you like best and feel the craze of Many Icons.

Features:
- 4 backgrounds to chose from,
- new, random layout each minute,
- date presentation,
- ambient mode,
- settings (seconds clock hand - 2 types, date on / off, background color).

Designed for Android Wear.
Supported smartwatches: LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, Motorola Moto 360, Sony SmartWatch 3, Asus ZenWatch, Samsung Gear Live.
